to run:

from this directory:

1. npm install
2. npm start

This prototype uses npm and package-lock.json. Do not regenerate yarn.lock.

to build without launching Electron:

$ npm run build

to run the TypeScript compiler without emitting files:

$ npm run typecheck

to run the wrapper generator:

$ npm run gen

The generator rewrites src/graph/graph.ts and src/graph/renderIfs.ts. Inspect the
diff after running it; renderIfs generation still needs a modernization pass.
